## 🔧 How to Run Locally

1. Clone the project:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/s-gasaro/player-info-stats-app.git
cd player-info-stats-app

2. Install dependencies:
npm install

3. Start app
npm start


🌐 API Used

  TheSportsDB API
  Endpoint example:
    
    [TheSportsDB](https://www.thesportsdb.com/)

  Returns:
  
  strPlayer (name)
  
  strTeam
  
  strNationality
  
  strDescriptionEN (bio)


